quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,"Hol ko …ďee naamnandirta."
  78,2,"Ko fa'ati e kabaaru maw…óo."
  78,3,"Mbo…ďe luhri e mum o."
  78,4,"Alaa wona noon, ma…ďe nganndu."
  78,5,"Refti yaama …ďe nganndu."
  78,6,"Mbela min mba…óaani lesdi nda…ó…óudi heblaandi."
  78,7,"E pelle …óe ngona peŇč…óe."
  78,8,"Min tagi on ku…ďe (noonooji)."
  78,9,"Min mba…ói …óoyngol mon fo'oftere."
  78,10,"Min mba…ói jehma o ko sutura."
  78,11,"Min mba…ói √Īalawma ko yiilaraade nguure."
  78,12,"Min mahi dow mon(sanamuuji )jee…ói…ói ca…ótu…ói."
  78,13,"Min mba…ói lampu jalbu…óoc(a…ótu…óa) ku…ď…ďam."
  78,14,"Min tellini ummo e duule ndiyam njuppajam sanne."
  78,15,"Ngam min njaltina heen gabbe e pu…ói."
  78,16,"E gese ne piilandir…óe."
  78,17,"Pellet, ko √Īalaande Seerndindiro ngon, laatinooma ko sa'atinaa."
  78,18,"√Ďande allaadu ndu wutta ma on ngardu pelle pelle."
  78,19,"Kammu on udditee mbo laato dame dame."
  78,20,"Pelle …óe njahnaa …óe ngonta merere."
  78,21,"Pellet jayngol jahannama wonti tommborde."
  78,22,"Nge wonani bew…ďe …ďe ruttorde."
  78,23,"Ko …ďe √Īii…ďo…ďe toon dummunaaji."
  78,24,"…ďe mee…óata toon …ďuu…ďol wona ndiyam …ďuu…ď…óam."
  78,25,"Si wona pat…óam ∆īii∆īiiri."
  78,26,"Njobdi hawrundi e ko…ďe ngonno ko."
  78,27,"Pellet …ďe ngoniina …ďe njoortaaki haasboore nih."
  78,28,"∆Āe njeddi aayeeje amen jeddugol."
  78,29,"Kala hu'unde min tonngirii nde binndol."
  78,30,"Mee…óe min …ďeydanta on si wona lepte."
  78,31,"Pellet na woodani hul…ďe Alla …ďe da…óirde."
  78,32,"Ko gese e inabeeje."
  78,33,"E (rew…ďe)∆īoolnu…ďe gi∆īiraa…ďe."
  78,34,"E ka'aseeje (sanngara) keew…óe."
  78,35,"∆Āe nanataa ndeer toon haala mehre, wonaa ko bakkondiŇčta."
  78,36,"Ko njo…ďdi ummaade e joom e dokke ke∆ī…óe."
  78,37,"joom kammu e leydi e ko woni hakkunde mu'en jurmtoo…óo mbo …ďe ngala e mum haala."
  78,38,"√Ďande jibriil ummii tawa malayka en na mba…ói sappeeji …ďe haalata si wona mbo Alla sakkitani o haala ko feewi."
  78,39,"Ko oon woni √Īalawma goongo kala paalaa…óo da…óde nanngira joomiiko ruttorde."
  78,40,"Min njeertinii on lepte …ďadii…óe √Īande aade ndaari ko juu…óe mum mba…óno ke'efeera o wi'a haaniina mi woniina lesdi."
